_sText: Hey, ever wanted a forest map with sunken ships and realistic barricading? Well this map is for you! A lagreg open, and dark map that truely makes ZM scarey again. Two buildings to camp on and barricade along with toher spots. Fps is pretty good, but there is one spot that dips into the low 30s, but nothing bad overall. Enjoy! Sicne this is the first beta, I expect some problems/bugs. Please email them to ASAP so I can fix it at Something1@earthlink.net
